OL,3,CPeople injured after ride 'fell to the
OL,4,Cfloor without stopping'
OL,6,FA number of people have been injured
OL,7,Ffollowing an incident on a ride at
OL,8,FWales' largest theme park.
OL,10,FThe Bounce ride at Oakwood Theme Park
OL,11,Fin Canaston Bridge, Pembrokeshire,
OL,12,Fexperienced a "programmed emergency
OL,13,Fstop procedure" whilst in mid-fall on
OL,14,FWednesday, 10 July, the owners park
OL,15,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,17,FIt added a number of people reported
OL,18,F"minor lower back pain" and had to be
OL,19,Fattended to by a team of in-house
OL,20,Ffirst aiders.
