OL,3,CPeople injured after ride 'fell to the
OL,4,Cfloor without stopping'
OL,6,FAn investigation is now under way into
OL,7,Fwhat happened on the ride, which re-
OL,8,Fopened at the park two years ago
OL,9,Ffollowing a #400,000 refurbishment.
OL,11,FBounce is a drop tower-style ride
OL,12,Fwhich takes guests around 45-metres
OL,13,Finto the air, before dropping them
OL,14,Fback down again.
OL,16,FThe park, which is the biggest in
OL,17,FWales, opened in 1987 on a family farm
OL,18,Fbefore being taken over by Spanish
OL,19,Fentertainment company Aspro Parks.
