OL,3,CPeople injured after ride 'fell to the
OL,4,Cfloor without stopping'
OL,6,FA visitor on board the ride when the
OL,7,Fincident happened said it "fell to the
OL,8,Ffloor without slowing down".
OL,10,FThey said school-age children were
OL,11,F"screaming and crying" as the ride
OL,12,F"went up and down a few times" before
OL,13,Fit "fell quickly to the ground from
OL,14,Fabout halfway up the tower".
OL,16,FThe guest, who did not want to be
OL,17,Fnamed, claimed the way the incident
OL,18,Fwas handled was "awful", and claimed
OL,19,Fthey only stopped and helped people
OL,20,Fwho "complained of pain or anything
OL,21,Fwrong".
