OL,3,CPeople injured after ride 'fell to the
OL,4,Cfloor without stopping'
OL,6,FThey added: "There have been no
OL,7,Fapologies from the park, they only
OL,8,Fgave information for guest relations
OL,9,Fbecause we asked for it to take it
OL,10,Ffurther after the fact we were told no
OL,11,Fmanagement was available."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Oakwood Theme Park
OL,14,Fsaid: "During operation on Wednesday,
OL,15,Four drop tower ride Bounce experienced
OL,16,Fa programmed Emergency Stop Procedure
OL,17,Fin response to the ride drop height
OL,18,Fduring a guest cycle.
