OL,3,CPeople injured after ride 'fell to the
OL,4,Cfloor without stopping'
OL,6,F"The stoppage which resulted in the
OL,7,Fpassenger gondola stopping in the ride
OL,8,Fbrakes was attended to by our park
OL,9,Fteam and the ride was lowered to the
OL,10,Fground where guests were able to
OL,11,Fdisembark.
OL,13,F"A number of guests reported minor
OL,14,Flower back pain immediately after the
OL,15,Foccurrence and were attended to by our
OL,16,Fonsite team of First Aiders, where
OL,17,Fassistance was provided. One group
OL,18,Fsought additional treatment locally,
OL,19,Fwhilst others continued their day at
OL,20,Fthe park.
